kroopt is a Lean 4 TLS 1.3 secure-channel library. It is designed to run on top
of iotakt (https://github.com/nabbisen/iotakt) for byte transport and beneath an
HTTP layer such as jemmet. Those dependencies are integrated at later milestones
and are not bundled here.

When the native crypto provider is added (M6), kroopt links HACL*/EverCrypt,
which carries its own license; that attribution will be added to this NOTICE at
that time.
